{"word":"G3309 - μεριμνάω - merimnáō - mer-im-nah'-o - Be careful","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μεριμνάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">merimnáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">mer-im-nah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be careful</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கவலைப்படு"},{"paragraph":"to be anxious; to be troubled with cares"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3308 - μέριμνα - mérimna - mer'-im-nah/3308\">G3308</a>; to <i>be anxious</i> about: - (be, have) care (-ful), take thought.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G275/275\">G275</a>, <a href=\"#/G3308/3308\">G3308</a>, <a href=\"#/G3309/3309\">G3309</a>, <a href=\"#/G4305/4305\">G4305</a>"}]}